      "type": "text",
      "title": "Loki Query Explorer - Common Patterns",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Loki Query Explorer & Templates\n\n## Common Query Patterns\n\n### By Service\n```\n{log_source=\"$log_source\", service_name=\"$service_name\"}\n```\n\n### By Level\n```\n{log_source=\"$log_source\"} | json | level=~\"error|warning\"\n```\n\n### By Pattern\n```\n{log_source=\"$log_source\"} |~ \"pattern\"\n```\n\n### By Rate (Errors)\n```\nrate(count_over_time({log_source=\"$log_source\", level=\"error\"}[5m])[5m:1m])\n```\n\n### Service Distribution\n```\ntopk(20, sum by(service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\\\"$log_source\\\"}[15m])))\n```"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 6
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Logs in Selected Scope",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({log_source=\"$log_source\", service_name=~\"$service_name\"}[6h]))"
        }
      ],
